gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bulls 105, 76ers 92
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bulls defeated the 76ers, 105-92, and improved to 15-19 on the year. DeMar DeRozan led Chicago with 24 points, six rebounds, and four assists as Coby White (20 points, eight rebounds) and Andre Drummond (15 points, 23 rebounds) totaled 35 points. Tyrese Maxey led the 76ers with 20 points and seven assists. Philadelphia moves to 22-10 on the season.
